text:
...Producer?
Don't you get tired working so hard?

Ah.. sorry, I'm fine.
You can go ahead and leave when you want, Mamimi.

Alriiight
... I'm going to grab a drink.

Want a drink?
Your mug has been empty for a while now.

Oh, those baked sweets, you don't mind...?
Haha, this is more luxurious than I deserve...!

Fufuu... and ater this there aren't any photo shoots
or costume fittings, so be sure you eat plenty.
